reviews.review_text: Great Kick Off Show Thanx Greg, Brion, and SirMick.  Wonderful sounding audience recording.  Everything nicely played.  First set very punchy, great NYE start.  I liked Foolish out of Miracle.  Nice quiet parts for He's Gone and Lovelight.  As an alternate burn you can put China>Rider at end of disc I set I.  The rest of set II is then on it's own disc.  You need only 2 discs then.  I say check it out.  I have been waiting over twenty years to hear this again.  I so appreciate it.  I am playing Space thru Lovelight on my radio show this week.  Peace
